The Federazione Giovanile Socialista Italiana has existed as our youth organisation since the turn of the century. Though nominally a youth organisation, it existence has been primarily to act as a 'Cadre School' for aspiring members of the party. With our duties expanded, however, we can begin utilising the youth organisation as a means to both aid the youth as well as help educate the future generations on socialism.

